title: Infant mortality rate in Malawi 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Deaths per 1,000 live births, containing a total of 11 data points.
Overall Deaths per 1,000 live births has decreased over the Year.
Deaths per 1,000 live births is slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2018.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Deaths per 1,000 live births, of value 59.2 was reached at Year 2008
Minimum Deaths per 1,000 live births about 35.3 was reached at Year 2018
